postquantumcryptoengine
------------------------------------------
Extension to the bctoolbox lib providing Post Quantum Cryptography

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libbctoolbox1-5.4.116-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  liboqs9-0.15.0-1bl1
  libpostquantumcryptoengine-devel-5.4.115-1bl1
  libpostquantumcryptoengine1-5.4.115-1bl1
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-5.4.116-1bl1
  liboqs-devel-0.15.0-1bl1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/postquantumcryptoengine

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/postquantumcryptoengine/archive/refs/tags/5.4.115.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack postquantumcryptoengine-5.4.115-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./postquantumcryptoengine-5.4.115-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/postquantumcryptoengine-5.4.115-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/postquantumcryptoengine-5.4.115-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpostquantumcryptoengine1-5.4.115-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpostquantumcryptoengine-devel-5.4.115-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(postquantumcryptoengine)
  /usr/bin/pqcrypto-tester.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/postquantumcryptoengine.README
  /usr/share/doc/postquantumcryptoengine/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/postquantumcryptoengine/README.md

(libpostquantumcryptoengine1)
  /usr/bin/cygpostquantumcryptoengine-1.dll

(libpostquantumcryptoengine-devel)
  /usr/include/postquantumcryptoengine/crypto.h
  /usr/include/postquantumcryptoengine/crypto.hh
  /usr/lib/cmake/postquantumcryptoengine/PostQuantumCryptoEngineConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/postquantumcryptoengine/PostQuantumCryptoEngineConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/postquantumcryptoengine/PostQuantumCryptoEngineTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/postquantumcryptoengine/PostQuantumCryptoEngineTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libpostquantumcryptoengine.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/postquantumcryptoengine.pc

